<h2>About v2.3.5 Update</h2>
<ul>
<li>✨ New Features

<ul>
<li>Added <code>Show additional menu items</code> option.</li>
</ul></li>
<li>⚡️ Improvements

<ul>
<li>Migrated to Swift 6.</li>
<li>Made it possible to display operating system information even when the macOS version is hidden.</li>
<li>Updated the window behavior to be hidden in Mission Control.</li>
<li>Sparkle Framework has been updated.</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p>
